title: Ep. #21 (ft. Co-Host Peniel) | SUNMI, EVERGLOW, and PENIEL
description:
In this week’s episode, we discuss SUNMI's “LALALAY” (4:21), EVERGLOW's “Adios” (8:14), and PENIEL's “Flip ft. Beenzino”(14:00). Don't miss Peniel's story of meeting Uncle Zino (Beenzino) and the downfall of underestimating one’s dart skills. Also, an extra special signed BTOB giveaway! Make sure to subscribe to @daebakshow (IT’S FREE) and leave us a comment, rating and/or review on Apple Podcasts, Spotify, Soundcloud, or YouTube. Connect with us on all social media platforms @daebakshow and at https://divestudios.io/show/daebakshow/! YouTube Bonus Content: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QqP21POP9eA&t=6s  #sunmi #everglow #peniel #beenzino #ericnam #daebakshow
